observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Mayor:
• require the Appraisal and Disposal Committee to provide the necessary information lacking in the IIRUP for the proper matching of the unserviceable properties carried in the PPE account;
• submit to the Audit Team the duly accomplished IIRUP together with its supporting documents;
• cause the immediate disposal of the unserviceable properties in order to maximize any realizable value from their disposal by sale in accordance with the existing regulations;
• require the Municipal Accountant to prepare the necessary adjusting entries for the derecognition of the unserviceable properties upon disposal based on Paragraph 82 of IPSAS 17 for the fair presentation of the financial statements pursuant to Paragraph 27 of IPSAS 1; and
• ensure that the disposal of property either thru public bidding or negotiated sale is properly documented and duly authorized.
